title: Google\Cloud\Retail\V2\RejoinUserEventsRequest\UserEventRejoinScope
name: UserEventRejoinScope
description:
The scope of user events to be rejoined with the latest product catalog.

If the rejoining aims at reducing number of unjoined events, set UserEventRejoinScope to UNJOINED_EVENTS. If the rejoining aims at correcting product catalog information in joined events, set UserEventRejoinScope to JOINED_EVENTS. If all events needs to be rejoined, set UserEventRejoinScope to USER_EVENT_REJOIN_SCOPE_UNSPECIFIED.

Protobuf type google.cloud.retail.v2.RejoinUserEventsRequest.UserEventRejoinScope
